<div class="container">

<!-- header container -->
	<div class="header-container">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-6">
				<h1>Herbivore Burgers</h1>
				<h4>For the animals, for our planet, for your health.</h4>
				<hr>
				<p>There are more vegan options in our times than ever before - soy, tempeh, mushroom, bean burgers. Biologically, humans don't need to consume animal flesh or secretions to survive. Yet we continue to consume them because we live in a society where it is <a href="http://www.cowspiracy.com/">socially acceptable</a> to do so. We make all <a href="https://www.earthlinged.com/30excuses/">kinds of justifications</a> for continuing to support an industry that greatly degrades and takes the lives of animals. Do some research about the impact of livestock farming <a href="https://www.peta.org/issues/animals-used-for-food/meat-environment/">on the environment</a> and the impact of animal products <a href="https://www.cancer.org/latest-news/world-health-organization-says-processed-meat-causes-cancer.html">on your health</a>.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-6">	
				<img id="cow-image" src="/assets/img/cow.jpeg">
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

<!-- container where burgers will dynamically populate -->
	<div class="burger-container">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-6">
				<h3>Burgers to be eaten</h3>
				<hr>
				<ul>
  					{{#each burgers}}
  						{{#unless devoured}}
  							<li class="individual-burger">{{ this.burger_name }} <button class="btn btn-light eat-button" data-id="{{ this.id }}">Eat it</button></li>
  						{{/unless}}
  					{{/each}}
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-6">
				<h3>Burgers eaten</h3>
				<hr>
				{{#each burgers}}
					{{#if devoured}}
					<li class="individual-burger">{{ this.burger_name }} </li>
					{{/if}}
				{{/each}}
			</div>
		</div>

	</div>

<!-- form container -->
	<div class="form-container">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-8 center-element">
				<h2>Add a burger</h2>
		
		  			<div class="form-group">
		    			<label for="burger_name">Enter the name of the burger that you would like below: </label>
		    			<input class="input-lg form-control" id="burger_input" type="text" name="burger">
		  			</div>

		  			<button id="submit-button">Add burger</button>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-4 idea-list">
				<ul>
					<li id="head-list">Vegan Burger Ideas</li>
					<hr>
					<li>Tempeh Bacon Burger</li>
					<li>Mushroom Burger</li>
					<li>Beyond Meat Burger</li>
					<li>Veggie Burger</li>
					<li>Cashew Cheeseburger</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>

	</div>

</div>